<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Document</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="css/about.css" />
    <link
      rel="stylesheet"
      href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/7.0.1/css/all.min.css"
      integrity="sha512-2SwdPD6INVrV/lHTZbO2nodKhrnDdJK9/kg2XD1r9uGqPo1cUbujc+IYdlYdEErWNu69gVcYgdxlmVmzTWnetw=="
      crossorigin="anonymous"
      referrerpolicy="no-referrer"
    />
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="about-page">
      <div class="about-header">
        <div class="logo">
          <img
            src="https://s3-ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/foodvista.1/7b92391c-fce4-44d5-84a3-1541c4b73e96.png"
            alt="logo"
          />
        </div>
        <div class="navigator">
          <a href="/menu">Menu</a>
          <a href="/corporate">Corporate</a>
          <a href="/about">About</a>
          <a href="/blogs">Blogs</a>
        </div>
        <div class="header-icons">
          <a href="/cart" style="color: inherit; position:relative; display:inline-flex; align-items:center;">
  <i class="fa-solid fa-cart-shopping"></i>
  <% if (typeof cartItemCount !== 'undefined' && cartItemCount > 0) { %>
    <span style="position:absolute; top:-8px; right:-10px; min-width:16px; height:16px; border-radius:999px; background:#ef4444; color:#fff; font-size:10px; line-height:16px; text-align:center; padding:0 4px; font-weight:700;"><%= cartItemCount %></span>
  <% } %>
</a>
          <% if (currentUser) { %>
            <a href="/orders" style="text-decoration:none; color:inherit;">Orders</a>
            <form action="/auth/logout" method="POST" style="display:inline; margin:0;">
              <button type="submit" class="header-order-btn" style="width:auto; height:auto; padding:8px 12px;">Logout</button>
            </form>
          <% } else { %>
            <a href="/auth/login" style="text-decoration:none; color:inherit;">Log In</a>
            <a href="/auth/signup" style="text-decoration:none; color:inherit;">Sign Up</a>
          <% } %>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="about-content">
        <div class="content-box">
          <div>
            <h1 class="content-heading"><b>BOWLS BEYOND <span class="span-content">BORDERS</span></b></h1>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h4  class="span-content">This is our belief.</h4>
          </div>
          <div>
            <p>
              Global cuisine doesn't belong behind velvet ropes. <br />
              The world's most iconic flavours — whether it's a bold Indian
              curry, <br />
              a rich Italian ragu, or a comforting continental classic — <br />
              should be part of your every day.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <p>
              Not an occasion. Not a luxury. <br />
              Just lunch. Or dinner. <br />
              Or a craving at 3pm.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <p>
              You shouldn't need a passport, a reservation, <br />
              or a big night out to taste something unforgettable. <br />
              You shouldn't have to choose between convenience and craft. <br />
              Or between flavour and freshness.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h2  class="span-content">
              So we bring the world to your table. <br />
              One bowl at a time.
            </h2>
          </div>
          <div>
            <p>
              Inspired by well-loved recipes from Tokyo to Tuscany. <br />
              Cooked only when you order. <br />
              Served hot, fresh, and priced for your everyday.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <p>
              And because the world is always cooking up something new, <br />
              our menu changes every week — <br />
              so there's always a new craving to discover.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <p>
              No pretence. No fine print. <br />
              What you get with us is just <span  class="span-content">bowls, beyond borders.</span>
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="about-footer">
        <div class="footer-all-links">
          <div class="footer-links-box">
            <img
              src="https://s3-ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/foodvista.1/7b92391c-fce4-44d5-84a3-1541c4b73e96.png"
              alt=""
            />
            <p style="margin: 15px 0">
              Bringing you fresh, global cuisine delivered right to your door.
              Every bowl tells a story of flavor, quality, and care.
            </p>
            <div class="social-media">
              <i class="fa-brands fa-instagram"></i>
              <i class="fa-brands fa-facebook-f"></i>
              <i class="fa-brands fa-twitter"></i>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="footer-links-box">
            <h2>Quick Links</h2>
            <a href="">Menu</a>
            <a href="">Locations</a>
            <a href="">About Us</a>
            <a href="">Corporate Ordering</a>
            <a href="">Bulk Order</a>
            <a href="">Blogs</a>
          </div>
          <div class="footer-links-box">
            <h2>Support</h2>
            <a href="">Returns & Refunds</a>
            <a href="">Privacy Policy</a>
            <a href="">Terms</a>
          </div>
          <div class="footer-links-box">
            <h2>Contact Us</h2>
            <div>
              <div class="footer-contact-us">
                <i class="fa-solid fa-location-dot"></i>
                <p>
                  Freshmenu, Sri Vaaru Plaza, Ground Floor, 19th Main Road Next
                  to ProBike HSR Layout 1st sector Bangalore 560102
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="footer-contact-us">
                <i class="fa-regular fa-envelope"></i>
                <div class="email-links">
                  <p class="email">order@freshmenu.com</p>
                  <p class="email">grievance@freshmenu.com</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <p>Office Hours:</p>
            <p>Monday - Friday (9:00 AM - 6:00 PM)</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="footer-rights">
          <p>
            &copy;2026 TheFoodTruck. All rights reserved. Made with ❤️ for food
            lovers everywhere.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>





